ublished>2024-11-27T10:44:56-05:00</published><updated> 2024-11-27T10:44:56-05:00</updated><title>寻找物品的最佳蓝牙追踪器</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Chipolo 卡点和 Tile Slim 旁边带有 AirTag 的钥匙圈。&quot; src =“https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/aGWKtAmBktwRL-yR01QeGypcqEI=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x 873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72403263/vsong_220323_5100_0005.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;蓝牙追踪器有各种形状和尺寸。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Victoria Song / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;对于我们这些似乎永远不知道钥匙、钱包和遥控器去了哪里的人来说。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt; a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23769840/best-bluetooth-trackers&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23769840/best-bluetooth-trackers" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23769840/best-bluetooth-trackers</id><author><name>宋茜</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-11-27T10:41:46-05:00</published><updated> 2024-11-27T10:41:46-05:00</updated><title> Uber 人工智能标签</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;由数据点组成的大脑的照片插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/BZCfFgyO5rXAwTiHm310nP9NM3I=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73751260/STK_414_AI_C.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;FoGbE1&quot;>;Uber 正在利用零工进入人工智能标签业务，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.bloomberg .com/news/articles/2024-11-26/uber-expands-into-ai-data-labeling-using-gig-coders-for-hire&quot;>;&lt;em>;彭博&lt;/em>;报告&lt;/a>;。这表明这家叫车和送货公司有兴趣扩展其独立承包商驱动的业务模式，以满足快速增长的机器学习和大语言模型领域的需求。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;Dia6BR&quot;>;公司新&lt;a href=&quot;https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.uber.com%2Fus%2Fen%2Fscaled-solutions%2F&amp;re ferrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2024%2F11%2F27%2F24307360%2Fuber-scaled-solutions-ai-labeling-workforce&quot; rel=&quot;sponsored nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;“规模化解决方案”部门&lt;/a>;声称，它可以使用其平台将企业与“细致入微的分析师、测试人员和独立数据运营商”联系起来。它是内部团队的延伸，其成员位于美国和印度，负责新功能测试和其他任务，例如将餐厅菜单转换为 Uber Eats 优食选择。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;Rzyv6V&quot;>;Uber 已经在使用人工智能并将机器学习用于自己的业务，现在......&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/27/24307360/uber-scaled-solutions-ai-labeling-workforce&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/27/24307360/uber-scaled-solutions-ai-labeling-workforce" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/27/24307360/uber-scaled-solutions-ai-labeling-workforce</id><author><name>奥马尔·沙基尔</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-11-27T10:23:55-05:00</published><updated> 2024-11-27T10:23:55-05:00</updated><title>您已经可以获得的最佳黑色星期五优惠</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;从蓝色购物车中飘出的各种黑色星期五促销产品的插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/tTpqzUgnqWUqqLz0GocYRLaqsqA=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox- cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73719439/247350_CMBF_2024_EWinataBlackFriday_2040x1360.15.png&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Elen Winata for The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;从降噪耳机到机器人吸尘器和 4K OLED 电视，已经有很多产品可供选择。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;一href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24293826/best-early-black-friday-deals-2024-amazon-walmart-buy-target-tech-sale&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p >; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24293826/best-early-black-friday-deals-2024-amazon-walmart-buy-target-tech-sale" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24293826/best-early-black-friday-deals-2024-amazon-walmart-buy-target-tech-sale</id><author><name>边缘人员</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-11-27T10:00:00-05:00</published><updated> 2024-11-27T10:00:00-05:00</updated><title> The Verge 为妈妈们准备的 2024 年节日礼物指南</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;蓝色天鹅绒背景上送给妈妈的礼物的生动照片。&quot; src =“https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/L2nejbjX4NxW2Wp0lYPqhnfZ-yQ=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cd n.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73751171/247215_Holiday_GG_2024_AKrales_MOMS_LEDE_2040x1360.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;照片：Amelia Holowaty Krales / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;从智能烤箱和日历到变色指甲油，以下是我们今年最喜欢送给妈妈的一些小玩意和商品.&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24224046/best-gift-ideas-mom-holiday-unique-2024-tech-gadgets&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24224046/best-gift-ideas-mom-holiday-unique-2024-tech-gadgets" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24224046/best-gift-ideas-mom-holiday-unique-2024-tech-gadgets</id><author><name>希娜·瓦萨尼</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-11-27T09:53:34-05:00</published><updated> 2024-11-27T09:53:34-05:00</updated><title> Starlink 的直接到蜂窝卫星服务是第一个获得 FCC 批准的</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;星链照片插图&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/KkgzmyMTzirxT3S12dAPdJ_xryo=/0x0:4896x3264/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73751110/2153819128.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Nikolas Kokovlis/NurPhoto via Getty Images&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;mjnuqa&quot;>;联邦通信委员会批准 SpaceX 使用其 Starlink 宽带卫星为 T-Mobile 客户提供直接连接-电话服务。 T-Mobile 许可证是卫星运营商和无线运营商之间首次获得 FCC 批准的合作，以提供来自太空的补充蜂窝覆盖。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;1QhfFV&quot;>;“委员会认识到卫星到-设备连接可以支持关键的公共利益，包括无处不在的连接、从偏远地区访问 911 服务、技术进步和创新频谱使用，”&lt;a href=&quot;https://docs.fcc.gov/public/attachments/DA-24-1193A1.pdf&quot;>;FCC 在文件中表示&lt;/a>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;ywiH7E&quot;>; SpaceX 和 T-Mobile 宣布了这一消息 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/6/24263801/starlink-t-mobile-fcc-satellite-hurricane-helene&quot;>;10 月获得临时许可&lt;/a>;以提供 Starlink 卫星受影响地区的服务...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/27/24307394/starlink-spacex-tmobile-direct-to-cell-satellite-fcc-approval&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p >; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/27/24307394/starlink-spacex-tmobile-direct-to-cell-satellite-fcc-approval" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/27/24307394/starlink-spacex-tmobile-direct-to-cell-satellite-fcc-approval</id><author><name>杰西韦瑟贝德</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-11-27T09:38:02-05:00</published><updated> 2024-11-27T09:38:02-05:00</updated><title>你现在可以穿苹果跑鞋表情符号了</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Apple 的跑鞋表情符号旁边是反映其设计的现实运动鞋。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/7DDwncb_GqiBq1CcJHYQ0lugqso=/0x0:942x628/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73751063/apple_emoji_shoe1.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;Shoe 1 的设计灵感来自 Apple 的跑鞋表情符号。&lt;/em>; |图片：Jose Wong&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;chWVh3&quot;>;艺术家兼设计师 Jose Wong 将苹果的跑鞋表情符号变成了一款真正的运动鞋 &lt;a href=&quot;https://josewongworld.com/products /%F0%9F%91%9F&quot;>;现在可通过他们的网站购买&lt;/a>;，尺码从​​ 5 到 12 不等。通过 Wong 的 ABCD 品牌发布的 Shoe 1 会让您惊叹不已一双售价 219.90 美元，预计将在一周内开始发货。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;u9Z4Ix&quot;>;这款鞋的鞋面采用全粒面正绒面革制成，结合网布以提高透气性，而中底和鞋跟由轻质 EVA 泡沫制成，搭配聚氨酯边缘，提供舒适感和“全天支撑”。&lt;/p>; &lt;div id=&quot;GYkBp0&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;imageslider:12491960&quot;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;L0tQII&quot;>;Shoe 1 的橡胶外底采用 5% 的再生橡胶制成，内部的泡沫鞋垫带有电子印花引用 A(BCD)5 处理器 - 向 A 系列芯片致敬...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/27/24307338/jose-wong-running-abcd-shoe-1-apple-emoji-fashion-streetwear&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt; /p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/27/24307338/jose-wong-running-abcd-shoe-1-apple-emoji-fashion-streetwear" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/27/24307338/jose-wong-running-abcd-shoe-1-apple-emoji-fashion-streetwear</id><author><name>安德鲁·利泽夫斯基</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-11-27T09:30:00-05:00</published><updated> 2024-11-27T09:30:00-05:00</updated><title>三星 Galaxy S24 FE 评测：粉丝票价不够</title><content type="html">&lt;p>;S24 FE 感觉不太像“粉丝版”，而更像是零售定位的练习。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24305866/samsung-galaxy -s24-fe-review-camera-battery-screen&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24305866/samsung-galaxy-s24-fe-review-camera-battery-screen" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24305866/samsung-galaxy-s24-fe-review-camera-battery-screen</id><author><name>艾莉森·约翰逊</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-11-27T07:43:52-05:00</published><updated> 2024-11-27T07:43:52-05:00</updated><title>出于心理健康问题，TikTok 将屏蔽青少年的美颜滤镜</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;照片插图显示一个人的脸被盗用于深度伪造色情内容。&quot; src =“https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/pGSpxOS72NSKMhIwmzo49bxMPQQ=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x87 3/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73750751/STK419_DEEPFAKE_CVIRGINIA_E.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;Cath Virginia / The Verge |照片来自 Getty Images&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;X3K0Bz&quot;>;TikTok 对其部分美颜滤镜设置了年龄限制，以解决人们对它们如何影响青少年用户心理健康的担忧。 “未来几周”推出的一些更改包括防止 18 岁以下儿童使用某些改变外观的效果，以及扩展滤镜描述以指定滤镜在应用时调整的内容。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;Qs1BND&quot;>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://newsroom.tiktok.com/en-eu/updates-from-our-eu​​ropean-safety-forum-strengthening-safety-for-our-now-175-m-strong-european-community&quot;>;新闻稿称，年龄限制不适用于“设计得明显且有趣”的滤镜效果，例如添加动物耳朵或滑稽地夸大某些特征。这一变化可能旨在解决&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/3/2/23621751/bold-glamour-tiktok-face-filter-beauty-ai-ar-body-dismorphia&quot;>; Bold Glamour&lt;/a>; 等美化效果可以让用户获得更光滑的皮肤、更长的睫毛和更苗条的脸，而这些效果可能更难以察觉。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;nnAbpt&quot;>;Nikki Soo 博士，...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/27/24307314/tiktok-beauty-filter-effects -age-restriction-teens-wellbeing&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/27/24307314/tiktok-beauty-filter-effects-age-restriction-teens-wellbeing" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/27/24307314/tiktok-beauty-filter-effects-age-restriction-teens-wellbeing</id><author><name>杰西韦瑟贝德</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-11-27T06:15:27-05:00</published><updated> 2024-11-27T06:15:27-05:00</updated><title>不，Microsoft 不会使用您的 Office 文档来训练其 AI</title><content type="html"> &lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;屏幕上有大脑的计算机的照片插图。&quot; src =“https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/B-by8krU3bKTqIkIN2AowpO9Ne4=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/c dn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73750603/STK_414_AI_CHATBOT_R2_CVirginia_D.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;插图由 Cath Virginia / The Verge 绘制 |照片由 Getty Images 提供&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;SMOoO7&quot;>;微软表示，它不会使用 Microsoft 365 应用程序中的客户数据来训练其 AI 模型。澄清地址&lt;a href=&quot;https://answers.microsoft.com/en-us/msoffice/forum/all/is-copilot-scraping-my-word-documents/5d7509fb-13dd-4c55-b478-1e8fc1afe678&quot; >;网上流传的报告&lt;/a>;&lt;a href=&quot;https://x.com/nixcraft/status/1860530950041485565&quot;>;过去几周&lt;/a>;声称微软要求 Word 和 Excel 用户选择不培训该公司的人工智能系统。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id =&quot;Fz1i8y&quot;>;Microsoft Office 中的隐私设置会切换“&lt;a href=&quot;https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/microsoft-365-apps/privacy/connected-experiences?ocid=usoc_TWITTER_M365_spl100006741601683#connected-experiences-that-analyze-your-content&quot;>;可选连接体验&lt; /a>;”——一项帮助用户“搜索在线图片”或“查找在线可用信息”的功能，据介绍微软。这个开关默认是打开的，并且在披露中没有提及人工智能训练。同样，2024 年 10 月 21 日发布的 Microsoft 学习文档似乎通过描述一长串 &lt;a href=&quot;https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/microsoft-365-apps/privacy/connected-experiences?ocid=usoc_TWITTER_M365_spl100006741601683#connected-experiences-that-analyze-your-content&quot;>;已连接... &lt;/a>;&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/27/24307284/microsoft-debunks-office-ai-data-scraping-rumors&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/27/24307284/microsoft-debunks-office-ai-data-scraping-rumors" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/27/24307284/microsoft-debunks-office-ai-data-scraping-rumors</id><author><name>杰西韦瑟贝德</name></author></entry></feed>